snippet.title: Zen Garden - Musical VR Relaxation [Launch Trailer]
snippet.description:
Now released on gearvr gallery apps!
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/gear-vr/1078672635555366/

We're really happy to announce that our VR relaxation app Zen Garden is finished.
Whether you're on a long flight or just looking to discover the cozy musical instruments, we hope that Zen Garden will help you to relax.
